OL,3,CThe parents who have pledged to keep
OL,4,Ctheir kids smartphone-free
OL,6,FShe said: "The reason most parents end
OL,7,Fup giving their kids a smart phone is
OL,8,Fpeer pressure. They don't want their
OL,9,Fchild to be the one that's left out."
OL,11,FJoe heard about a growing movement of
OL,12,Fparents across the UK who were
OL,13,Fagreeing together to delay giving
OL,14,Ftheir child a phone.
