OL,3,CThe parents who have pledged to keep
OL,4,Ctheir kids smartphone-free
OL,6,FJoe said: "We thought if we can just
OL,7,Fget a few other parents on board then
OL,8,Fwe won't be the only ones. Having that
OL,9,Fsafety in numbers is really nice. It
OL,10,Fmeans we know for sure our children
OL,11,Fare not going to be the only ones not
OL,12,Fhaving a smart phone."
OL,14,FTheir children Tom and Meredith say
OL,15,Fthey understand the choice their
OL,16,Fparents have made.
