OL,3,CThe parents who have pledged to keep
OL,4,Ctheir kids smartphone-free
OL,6,FTom, aged nine, said: "My mum says
OL,7,Fthat once you see something you can't
OL,8,Funsee it, so you might get nightmares
OL,9,Fand stuff and I don't want to get
OL,10,Fnightmares."
OL,12,FHe added: "There's still plenty of
OL,13,Fother stuff you can do without a
OL,14,Fmobile phone like playing the guitar
OL,15,Fand being outside."
