OL,3,CThe parents who have pledged to keep
OL,4,Ctheir kids smartphone-free
OL,6,F"I'm hoping, maybe in the future,
OL,7,Fthere will be more choices but right
OL,8,Fnow there isn't and so I feel like the
OL,9,Fsafest thing we can do for our kids is
OL,10,Fto then just delay that until they are
OL,11,Fold enough because they are still
OL,12,Fchildren."
OL,14,FWoolacombe School has 174 children and
OL,15,F75 families have already signed up to
OL,16,Fthe pledge - but they say it certainly
OL,17,Fnot about being anti-technology.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
